SYNOPSIS

    In your source code:

     use Data::Dump::Patch::Deparse;
     use Data::Dump;
    
     dd(sub { [1,2] }); # now prints "sub { [1, 2] }" instead of "sub { ... }"

    On the command-line:

     % perl -MData::Dump::Patch::Deparse -MData::Dump -e'dd ...'

DESCRIPTION

PACKAGE VARIABLES

 $OPT_REMOVE_PRAGMAS

    Like in Data::Dmp.

 $OPT_PERL_VERSION

    Like in Data::Dmp.

SEE ALSO

    Data::Dump

